                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9797" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1109</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">613 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业之“心”如何激活乡村之“脉”：保良古村从衰败到振兴的转型实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How Entrepreneurial Spirit Revitalizes Rural Vitality: The Transformation of Baoliang Ancient Village from Decay to Sustainable Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘玲，刘珂丽，童泽林</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海南澄迈保良乡村旅游开发有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">26 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乡村振兴；返乡创业；资源整合；机会识别；商业模式设计</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rural Revitalization；Returnee Entrepreneurship；Resource Integration；Opportunity Recognition；Business Model Design</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以海南省澄迈县保良古村的振兴实践为主线，聚焦“返乡创业者如何联动多元主体、推动乡村全面振兴”这一核心问题，讲述了90后返乡创业青年王谋超如何带领团队，将一个人口流失、耕地撂荒、文化凋敝的空心村逐步转变为一个有生机活力、情感认同与机制支撑的现代化乡村。案例重点呈现了团队在利益机制构建、文化认同塑造、空间边界拓展与治理结构创新等方面的实践路径，揭示了返乡创业者作为关键行动者，如何联动多元主体，推动保良古村关系网络的修复与协作秩序的重建。本案例不仅有助于学生深入理解创业精神在乡村发展中的实践意义，提升其在复杂场域中整合资源、机会识别的综合能力，也为其他衰败的村庄提供了可借鉴的振兴启示，并为推动城乡要素流动与资源活化带来了经验借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study centers on the revitalization of Baoliang Ancient Village in Chengmai County, Hainan Province, with a particular focus on how a returnee entrepreneur mobilizes diverse stakeholders to drive comprehensive rural revitalization. It recounts how Wang Mouchao, a post-1990s returnee, led a team to transform a depopulated, agriculturally abandoned, and culturally declining &quot;hollow village&quot; into a vibrant, socially cohesive, and institutionally supported modern rural community. The case highlights the team&#39;s practical strategies in constructing interest-sharing mechanisms, fostering cultural identity, expanding spatial boundaries, and innovating governance structures. It demonstrates how the entrepreneur, as a core actor, coordinates heterogeneous actors and rebuilds relational ties and a collaborative order within the village. This case not only facilitates students’ in-depth understanding of the practical significance of entrepreneurial spirit in rural development, but also enhances their integrated capabilities in resource mobilization and opportunity recognition within complex contexts. Moreover, it offers valuable insights for the revitalization of other declining villages and provides empirical reference for promoting the flow of urban–rural factors and the activation of rural resources.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新创业管理》、《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业精神；资源整合；创业机会识别；商业模式画布；创业风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
